data.description:
Welcome to your ideal home! Step into this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasting captivating curb appeal. As you enter, the grandeur of high ceilings and a spacious hallway, guiding you to two bedrooms and your first full bath.
Prepare to be charmed as the floor plan unfolds to reveal the heart of the home—a stunning kitchen featuring rich wood cabinets, state-of-the-art stainless steel built-in appliances, and an expansive island. The adjoining living room boasts a ceiling design adorned with wood beams and comes equipped with a surround sound system.
Retreat to the master bedroom, nestled away for added privacy, complete with a generous walk-in closet, double vanity sinks, and a soothing rain shower head.
Step outside into your enchanting, fully landscaped backyard and unwind beneath the inviting pergola or savor the sunset on your covered patio porch. The backyard also offers the convenience of a dog run discreetly located on the side of the home. 
Schedule your showing today!
